{"tid":1267943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【引渡惡法】人民力量會址被爆門闖入 7.1示威物品受損","createTime":"2019-06-30T06:42:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T06:49:25.000Z","uid":48093,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ad95117ff5cfe345c6efb7c8abb023164a2ef169","tid":1267943,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T06:42:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190630/large/1561874852_05cb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190630%2Flarge%2F1561874852_05cb.png&h=46fa6461&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n民陣的7.1遊行舉行前夕，人民力量指其於九龍灣的會址於今日（30日）凌晨時份被不明人士爆門闖入，稱有關7.1遊行的示威物品損毀，人民力量強烈譴責有關行徑，直斥「在臨近政治敏感的日子，以粗暴低劣的手法，大肆破壞會址內的示威物資，打壓香港人的示威和表達自由。」<br />\n<br />\n人民力量發出新聞稿指，今日凌晨12時左右，其九龍灣會址遭人惡意破壞，指會址被不明人士爆門闖入，而早前準備的7.1遊行示威物品亦被損毀，地面更倒滿刺鼻難聞的液體，示威牌散滿一地，人民力量強烈譴責相關行徑。"},{"pid":"3d9f9c6a317cdd09319b249cdb2befdf550d8aa8","tid":1267943,"uid":99018,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T06:47:07.000Z","msg":"黑警與黑社會同在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9526cdfabf4da78d3bb6675ae9b99c30e0119e07","tid":1267943,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T06:49:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8pAyEOY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8pAyEOY.jpg&h=6abdede8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[ 備戰 ] 夢境作戰訓話 + 整合Post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1267323/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1267323/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n香港人到而家仲未識真正咁運用三角鐵馬<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1267307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1267307</a>"}]}